<topic id="l200-overview">
  <title><keyword keyref="lm-passage-l200-tm"/></title>
  <shortdesc>The first <keyword keyref="lm-edgeless-io-tm"/> 3D Co-Packaged Optics,  eliminating the
    shoreline bottleneck to deliver 32–64 Tbps of optical I/O per chip.</shortdesc>

  <body>

